{
  "name": "RPlog_Fall_From_Grace",
  "title": "Fall From Grace",
  "summary": "Aboard the YT-1300 Black Dragon, the charming, wounded Corellian Paul Nighman teases the young runaway Shenner and, giving in to a reckless impulse, kisses her, only for her to panic and punch him; dodging, he topples backward onto his already injured side. Mortified and trying to mask his pain, Paul later seeks Shenner out, apologizes, and offers her a no-strings comforting hug, which the overwhelmed seventeen-year-old accepts, breaking down in tears about how much has happened to her and her discomfort at being known as a girl. Their fragile moment is interrupted by the arrival of new crewmembers Tacra and her companion Tand, invited aboard by Skywalker, prompting Shenner to storm off to the cargo bay. Paul follows, and the two agree to bunk together in the hold for privacy. All the while Paul's blaster wound from Vermillion's blades worsens unnoticed, swelling purple as fever, thirst, and vertigo take hold. Determined not to alarm Shenner, Paul slips off the ship and staggers through the Palanhi City streets toward the Medical Center, finally collapsing unconscious on its floor.",
